summary: Adds a fully equipped Dwemer style house near lake Illinata
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a very large Dwemer style house near the edge of the lake. Currently it is the moment you get on you got it but I am currently working on the quest to get it.

It comes with:
A full and complete mine
A full forge
Enchanting table
Alchemy station
More storage than you could ever need
More mannequins then you would ever want
An epic throne room 
The best view you could possibly imagine

I am not the greatest interior decorator so if you have any ideas lay em on me. You know what if you have ANY ideas i will gladly accept them that dosen\\\'t mean ill put them in but ill try.

Happy gaming
author: pilchar
